Package: ramazon
Type: Package
Title: deploy your shiny app on Amazon AWS running a function
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-08-05
Author: Andrea Cirillo
Maintainer: Andrea Cirillo <andreacirilloac@gmail.com>
Description: the main aim of ramazon is to relieve the pain of publish shiny apps on Amazon EC2 instances.
This is obtained providing a single function, ramazon(), able to take care of everything needed in order to
install R, shiny-server and the user shiny app on a Ubuntu 14.0 server running on the Amazon EC2 instance.

